<p>The tile grid pattern contains a heading, a call to browse button and a grid layout of tiles; it is used to show a collection of news and/or events.</p>

<p>The tile pattern is a clickable, single-action item. It includes an image, title and description. It's ideally used for displaying an event or news item.</p>

<p>The description text should be 3 to 4 lines in length, or roughly 80 to 140 characters.</p>

